headline: Public Service Enterprise Group (NYSE:PEG) Reports Q1 Earnings with US$3,222 Million Sales
summary: Public Service Enterprise Group (NYSE:PEG) announced its first quarter 2025 earnings, showing growth in both sales and net income compared to the previous year.
